title: No end of season reward??
body:
I made it to Silver 5 on this account. With good honor standing. level 2 with 2 check points...
But no boarder.. No icon.. No ward skin like it said [here ](https://oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/page/end-season-rewards-2018).

Just wanted to know if I missed something or it was a bug.
